snippet: A judge ruled that One L. Goh, who is accused of killing seven people at a small Christian college in Oakland, Calif., is not mentally fit for trial.
abstract: California Judge Carrie Panetta rules that One L Goh, man accused of killing seven people at a small Christian college in Oakland, is not mentally fit for trial.
lead_paragraph: A judge ruled that One L. Goh, who is accused of killing seven people at a small Christian college in Oakland, Calif., is not mentally fit for trial.
